Class EditInfoC

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.elo.ix.client.EditInfoC
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EditInfoC
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

    Constants to read data for editing the indexing information of an archive entry

    See Also:
    EditInfo, Serialized Form

    • Field Summary

      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static EditInfoZ mbAll
      Deprecated. 
      This selector causes much data to be transfered over the network. Use a combination of EditInfoC.mb values instead, that explicitly define the amount of data to be returned. If only indexing information and document version data is of interest mbSordDocAtt or mbSord should be used.
